{
  "stem": "11075.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have to try to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then Schindler thought, you know, that-- but I couldn't, because they were watching the other gate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Plenty SS men.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they gave me, naked, you know, 50 on my behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To escape.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For a nice couple of weeks, I had black marks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Black marks, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A nurse was every day, every day trying to help me out, you know, in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a small hospital over there, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And nurses and something like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But all right, so I survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After a year, they liquidate the concentration camp, Jerozolimska.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we all went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Was already-- we-- I was already on the list, you know, to go to-- Schindler's list.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 19-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made-- in the ghetto, they made the list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In ghetto.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Banchur helped me and Schindler helped me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To me, they were-- they were very nice, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Besides, he was my cousin, and money, he had plenty from the factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He sold it, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because to the SS Men, Schindler said, listen, I don't care about the factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I want to help you, the SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The SS Men ask, how can you help us?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said-- he was very smart, Schindler-- I'll tell you how.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have the stores.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Polish people, they can't buy nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's empty.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if the factory-- I will run the factory, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They will have plenty pots and pans, and everybody will buy it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for the money, you can buy bullets and guns and everything what you need it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because without guns, without anything, you can't go into the toilet.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
